<!-- EN: <b>Manual activation signal confirmed</b>\n\n
Mechanoid Total Warfare Protocol X activated! All mechanoid units will receive battlefield enhancements:\n\n
• <b>Overdrive</b>: Some mechanoids are overloaded with massive energy injection for short periods\n
• <b>Optical Camo Disruption</b>: Random mechanoid units are equipped with optical camouflage modules, making them invisible on the battlefield.\n
• <b>Composite Armor Reinforcement Protocol</b>: Some units' protective capabilities are significantly enhanced.\n
• <b>Tactical Artillery Coordination Module</b>: Some units can summon turret support\n
• <b>Long Range Ballistics Optimization System</b>: Some units' weapon range is increased.\n\n
• <b>High Mobility Phase Shift Drive</b>: Some units' movement speed is greatly enhanced.\n\n
<b>Tactical Recommendations:</b>\n
- Prioritize EMP weapons\n
- Deploy sensors to detect invisible units\n
- Lay point defense systems to counter high-angle projectiles
 -->
  <NCL_TOTALWARFARE_MANUAL_TRIGGER_TEXT>&lt;b>手动激活信号已确认&lt;/b>\n\n\n机械族全面战争协议X已激活！所有机械单位将获得战场强化：\n\n\n• &lt;b>机械超载&lt;/b>：部分机械体因被注入大量能量而在短时间内超载\n\n• &lt;b>光学迷彩干扰装置&lt;/b>：随机单位机械体被赋予光学迷彩模块，使其从战场上隐身。\n\n• &lt;b>复合装甲增强协议&lt;/b>：部分单位的防护能力获得大幅增强。\n\n• &lt;b>远程战术协调单元&lt;/b>：部分单位可召唤炮塔支援\n\n• &lt;b>长距弹道优化模组&lt;/b>：部分单位的武器射程获得了增长。\n\n\n• &lt;b>超功率推进器&lt;/b>：部分单位的移动速度得到了大幅加强。\n\n\n&lt;b>战术建议：&lt;/b>\n\n- 优先使用EMP武器\n\n- 部署传感器探测隐形单位\n\n- 铺设点防御系统以反制高角投射物\n  </NCL_TOTALWARFARE_MANUAL_TRIGGER_TEXT>

