<!-- EN: You have successfully repaired this war beacon. Its massive structure looms over the wasteland like a slumbering beast, sending chills down your spine. As the core structure used by mechanoids to mark strategic coordinates, its activation means you will be exposed to their sight—more powerful, more deadly mechanoid forces will pour in, attempting to utterly destroy you.\n
But high risk comes with high reward. By analyzing the beacon's core data, you may crack the mechanoids' technological barriers and unlock cutting-edge technologies once beyond reach.\n
The choice is yours—remain silent for preservation, or ignite the war and face the unknown?\n
Activate it, activate the war. -->
  <NCL_WARBEACON_REACTIVATE_DESCRIPTION>你已成功修复这座战争信标，它庞大的构造在废土之上仿佛一尊沉眠的巨兽，令人不寒而栗。作为机械族用以标定战略坐标的核心建筑，它的激活意味着你将暴露于他们的视野之中——更强大、更致命的机械部队将陆续涌来，妄图将你彻底摧毁。\n\n但高风险亦伴随高回报。通过分析信标的核心数据，你有望破解机械族的技术壁垒，解锁曾经遥不可及的尖端科技。\n\n选择权在你手中——是沉默以保全，还是点燃战火，直面未知？\n\n开启它，开启战争。</NCL_WARBEACON_REACTIVATE_DESCRIPTION>
